Turns https://sourceforge.net/projects/aper/ into sendmail access db
- Filters out blank lines
- Filters out comment lines
- Filters out lines without an @
- Filters out lines without an RHS
- Filters out lines without an LHS
- Filters out lines with something.ourdomain on the RHS
- Filters out lines with ourdomain on the RHS if they are in our directory

make -f test.mk can be used to exercise sample data and an (old) copy of phishing_reply_addresses
